      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MALICIOUS (3) was a little disappointing last start at this track when 4th (30.77) over 525m. Goes very well at course and distance boasting four wins. Can make amends. OXLEY CHOICE (1) ran below best last time finishing fifth (17.91) over 300m at this track from Box 1. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. WOW GIRL (2) is a last start placegetter in a Grade 5, jumping from this box and finishing a 3 length second over 300m at this track. Boasts a strong record off this same box, including two wins and three placings from eight starts. Has the ability and looks a key chance. SPIN AROUND BLUE (7) racing over this course and distance brings the best out in him.",
